title: "I'm Really Good At Shakespeare"
description: Jacob has to defend one of his favorite bands Iron Maiden, and tells a story about him and his father. Jay makes fun of Christine for wanting Shakespeare on the new bookshelf. The guys discuss the immense knowledge of basketball the Kardashians must have.
